Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.96,0:01:34.66,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.66,0:01:37.76,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m so lucky that I can go\Nshopping with you today, Kaji!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.76,0:01:38.93,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What the?!  Isn’t this the\Nswimsuit section?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.93,0:01:41.30,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Please allow us to announce a\Ncall for a customer.\N{\c&H00E3FE&}What the?!  Isn’t this the\Nswimsuit section?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.30,0:01:42.30,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Please allow us to announce a\Ncall for a customer.\N\N\N{\c&H00E3FE&}Hey!  Hey!  How do you like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.30,0:01:43.60,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Mr. Yamazaki from Ibaragi City,\Nyour friend is waiting for you.\N\N\N{\c&H00E3FE&}Hey!  Hey!  How do you like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:47.67,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Mr. Yamazaki from Ibaragi City,\Nyour friend is waiting for you.\N{\c&H00E3FE&}Slow down, school girl.  You’re a little\Nyoung for something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.67,0:01:50.14,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Please come to Customer Service\Non the first floor.\N{\c&H00E3FE&}You’re just being an old\Nfuddy-duddy, Mr. Kaji.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.14,0:01:51.61,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Please come to Customer Service\Non the first floor.\N\N\N{\c&H00E3FE&}This is what’s in fashion these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.61,0:01:52.11,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is what’s in fashion these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.38,0:01:55.64,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.64,0:02:00.02,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m so anxious about this school trip.\NI just know we’ll have a great time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.02,0:02:01.32,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,And where are you going for the trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.32,0:02:03.59,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,O-ki-na-wa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.59,0:02:06.59,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,We’re even scheduled to go\Nscuba diving!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.26,0:02:08.76,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Scuba diving...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.39,0:02:11.50,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s been three years since\NI’ve gone diving.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.26,0:02:15.43,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Say, where did you go for\Nyour school trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.43,0:02:17.74,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, we didn’t have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.40,0:02:20.24,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 4,0:02:20.24,0:02:22.24,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Video Text,Because of the Second Impact.
