Dialogue: 3,0:02:21.95,0:02:24.99,Title (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Video Text,{\blur0.7)}{\pos(360,257)}MAGMA DIVER
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.41,0:02:30.55,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Whaaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.55,0:02:32.82,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I can’t go on the trip?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.55,0:02:34.35,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.35,0:02:35.45,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.45,0:02:36.79,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Because you’re on standby\Nfor combat duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.79,0:02:38.49,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You never told me anything about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.49,0:02:39.55,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I just told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.55,0:02:41.09,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Who in the hell decided that?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.09,0:02:43.59,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Me, the Operations Planning Manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.80,0:02:52.50,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hey, you!  Why don’t you stop slurping\Nthat tea and say something to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:53.87,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Be a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.87,0:02:57.71,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Actually, I kind of anticipated it\Nwould be like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.71,0:02:59.81,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,And you’ve already given up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.31,0:03:05.25,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Talk about pathetic.  There’s nothing\Nmore useless than a housebroken male.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.25,0:03:07.23,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Please don’t talk about me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:10.05,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I know how you must feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.05,0:03:12.05,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...but there’s no other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.05,0:03:16.63,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,There’s always the possibility that an\NAngel may attack while you’re away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.56,0:03:21.03,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s always “standby”!\NStandby, standby, standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.03,0:03:24.57,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,We’ve always got to be ready to\Ndefend against an enemy who may\Nor may not be coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.57,0:03:27.84,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Why don’t you try to find out where\Nthey are and attack them first?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:31.11,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,If we could do that we’d\Nhave already done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.11,0:03:34.64,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Look, think of this as an opportunity\Nto catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.64,0:03:37.35,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,While the rest of your class\Nis on the trip...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.35,0:03:39.61,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...the two of you can study.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.61,0:03:41.99,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Or do you think I don’t know\Nabout these?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.19,0:03:46.29,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,If you thought I wouldn’t know about\Nyour test scores unless you told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.29,0:03:50.36,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...you made a big mistake.  Finding out\Nwhat your grades are...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.36,0:03:51.74,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...is quite simple for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.26,0:03:56.00,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s ridiculous.  This school’s grades\Nare meaningless!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:59.57,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The old-fashioned numeric grading\Nscale system you use on your\Nexams means nothing to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.57,0:04:02.04,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,When in Rome, do as the Romans do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.04,0:04:04.41,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You could at least try to adjust to\NJapanese school life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.41,0:04:06.85,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Noooooooo way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.78,0:04:12.22,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Asuka, I’ll bring you some souvenirs!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:15.88,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, it’s just too bad for you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.88,0:04:18.36,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Don’t feel bad, I’ll have enough\Nfun for both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.13,0:04:29.91,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Post the survey data on Mt. Asama\Nfrom Balthasar to Melchior\Nas soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.81,0:04:39.24,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,A school trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.24,0:04:41.64,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That’s pretty casual behavior for\Ntimes like these.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.64,0:04:46.26,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, it’s because the times are so\Nhard that they want to have a little\Nfun while they can.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.96,0:04:56.09,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.76,0:04:58.33,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Studying physics.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.33,0:05:01.10,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’re such an obedient\Nstudent, Mr. Big Shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.10,0:05:03.70,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, I’d have to anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.50,0:05:06.17,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.17,0:05:09.54,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Since I can’t go scuba diving in\NOkinawa, I’m going to do it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.54,0:05:11.17,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.17,0:05:13.41,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What’re you working on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:14.44,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Lemme see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.81,0:05:18.19,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You can’t solve an easy\Nproblem like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.18,0:05:20.92,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,There!  Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.92,0:05:22.82,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s so easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.82,0:05:26.73,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,How can you solve a difficult problem\Nlike this and not make good grades\Non your tests?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.59,0:05:30.93,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Because I couldn’t figure out\Nwhat the questions said.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:34.20,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You mean you couldn’t read the\Nquestions in Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.20,0:05:37.17,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Right, I haven’t learned all\Nof the Kanji yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.17,0:05:39.60,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I didn’t have to study it in college.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.60,0:05:40.37,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,College?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.37,0:05:42.47,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yeah, I graduated last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.97,0:05:45.94,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What does this one say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.94,0:05:48.44,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s about thermal expansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.44,0:05:51.79,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Thermal expansion?  Kid stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:58.80,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,To put it simply, things expand when\Nthey get hot and shrink when\Nthey get cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:01.32,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, it sounds easy enough in theory...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:05.79,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,So, if I were to warm up my bust, do\Nyou think they’d grow bigger?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.79,0:06:08.73,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,How would I know such a thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.73,0:06:10.51,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’re such a boring little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:33.00,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Looky, looky, Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.82,0:06:35.77,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Back Roll Entry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.37,0:06:52.31,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This just isn’t clear enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.31,0:06:55.24,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,But the report from the Mt. Asama\NEarthquake Research Lab\Nwould indicate...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.24,0:06:56.91,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...that we should take a closer look\Nat this shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.91,0:06:58.98,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Of course, we can’t ignore this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:00.36,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What’s MAGI’s judgment?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:02.52,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Fifty-fifty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:03.69,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Is someone there yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.69,0:07:06.29,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Captain Katsuragi’s already on site.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.69,0:07:12.96,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’ve gone too deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.96,0:07:15.24,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Not yet, descend another 500, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.10,0:07:24.31,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Depth 1200.  The pressure resistant\Npartition is cracking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.01,0:07:26.27,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Ms. Katsuragi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.27,0:07:29.08,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,If it breaks, we’ll pay for the damage.\N200 more, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.58,0:07:34.03,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,We’re monitoring a reaction!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:37.39,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Begin analysis!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.39,0:07:38.89,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.06,0:07:49.47,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The probe has imploded due to\Nthe extreme pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:51.10,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Did you get a result?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.10,0:07:53.02,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Just barely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.02,0:07:54.50,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The pattern is blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.50,0:07:56.01,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Then there’s no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.01,0:07:57.74,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s an Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:08:00.34,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,From this point forward, this laboratory\Nwill be completely sealed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.34,0:08:02.48,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s under NERV’s jurisdiction now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.48,0:08:04.68,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Any and all access to the outside\Nworld is prohibited.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.68,0:08:08.09,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,All records pertaining to the events of\Nthe past six hours are classified.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:13.73,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I need an A-17 from Commander Ikari,\Ntop priority!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:16.09,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Watch what you’re saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.09,0:08:17.56,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is an open line.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.56,0:08:19.32,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.32,0:08:21.63,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Switch me to a scrambled line.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.63,0:08:23.40,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,A-17?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.40,0:08:25.00,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,An offensive attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:26.43,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.43,0:08:28.40,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Unacceptable, it’s too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:31.01,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten what happened\Nfifteen years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.01,0:08:37.55,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is our chance to move from a\Nperpetually defensive posture to\Nan offensive one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.55,0:08:39.78,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The risk is enormous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.78,0:08:45.69,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,However, I’m sure you’re aware how\Nimportant it is to obtain a living Angel\Nas a sample, aren’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.69,0:08:47.79,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,We will not tolerate failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.66,0:08:51.36,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Failure?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:54.27,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,If we fail, it will result in the extinction\Nof the entire human race.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.50,0:08:57.44,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Are you really going to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.33,0:09:00.34,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is an Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.34,0:09:04.84,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes, it’s something like a chrysalis\Nprior to reaching the adult stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.84,0:09:08.44,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This operation’s prime objective is to\Ncapture this Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:11.98,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,We must capture it alive and in\Na form as close to its original\Nstate as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:13.21,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,And if we fail?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.21,0:09:15.45,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Then you must destroy it immediately.\NDo you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:16.15,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.15,0:09:17.62,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The designated pilot for the\Nactual operation is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:20.00,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hey, let me!  I dive!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:22.89,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade In & Out,{\fad(170,170)}I know it’s going to be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:24.79,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:26.43,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You will carry out the mission\Nusing Unit 02.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.43,0:09:29.38,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Sure!  It’ll be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.93,0:09:30.90,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,And me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:35.10,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The special equipment we’ll be using\Nisn’t standardized for use on\Nthe Unit 00 prototype.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.10,0:09:38.14,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Rei and Unit 00 will remain at\Nheadquarters on standby.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:39.11,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.11,0:09:40.84,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Oh, too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.84,0:09:42.45,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You don’t get to go to the hot springs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.08,0:09:47.15,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Now that an A-17 has been ordered,\Nwe must scramble immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.15,0:09:48.08,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.08,0:09:49.59,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:56.19,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This heat-resistant plug suit doesn’t\Nseem any different from our\Nregular ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.72,0:09:58.60,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Press the switch on your right wrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.56,0:10:01.54,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.13,0:10:04.04,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.77,0:10:06.54,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Unit 02 is also ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.30,0:10:09.18,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.18,0:10:11.15,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I don’t believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.07,0:10:14.91,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That suit’s designed to protect you from\Nheat, pressure and nuclear radiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.91,0:10:17.08,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is Type-D equipment, for combat\Nunder extreme environmental duress.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.58,0:10:20.25,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Is that my Unit 02?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.65,0:10:23.92,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,No way!  I quit!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.92,0:10:26.52,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I don’t want to appear in public\Nin this dorky outfit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:29.09,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is the sort of thing Shinji’s for!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.09,0:10:30.59,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m so disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.23,0:10:33.90,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I was anticipating seeing Asuka’s\Ngallant figure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:35.40,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.76,0:10:41.14,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I can’t let Mr. Kaji see me in\Nthis awful looking thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.14,0:10:42.37,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,We’re having problems?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.37,0:10:43.88,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:46.37,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.37,0:10:48.08,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’ll go in Unit 02.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.25,0:10:54.13,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,No, I don’t want you touching\Nmy Unit 02!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.85,0:10:57.23,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’d rather do it than let her\Ntake my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:02.36,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m sorry about the look.\NPlease, forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:18.18,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Eva Units 01 and 02 have arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:20.98,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Have both units stand by in position.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.98,0:11:23.78,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Move in the laser bore and\Nready the crane.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.78,0:11:25.28,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.18,0:11:30.55,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hey, isn’t Kaji here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.55,0:11:33.36,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That male buffoon won’t be coming.\NHe’s got no business here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:37.46,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Oh, damn!  I wanted him to\Nsee how great I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:40.06,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,An A-17 has been ordered.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.06,0:11:42.96,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That includes the freeze of\Nall current assets.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.96,0:11:46.13,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I assume that means that some people\Nwill be getting into a bit of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.13,0:11:47.90,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Why didn’t you stop them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.90,0:11:49.76,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I had no excuse for stopping it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.76,0:11:51.84,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This order is an official one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.84,0:11:55.68,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,But, surely you must know that if NERV\Nfails, the whole world will perish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.68,0:11:58.21,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,They’re not that arrogant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:03.12,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What are... those?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.12,0:12:05.82,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The UN and the Air Force will be\Non standby alert...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.82,0:12:07.82,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...until this mission has been completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.82,0:12:09.42,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Will they help us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.42,0:12:11.49,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,No, they’re here to clean up...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.49,0:12:13.23,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...in case we fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.13,0:12:15.43,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.43,0:12:19.24,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,They will employ N2 depth charges\Nto destroy the Angel and us with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:21.00,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That’s dreadful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.00,0:12:23.54,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Who would order something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.54,0:12:25.04,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Commander Ikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.31,0:12:33.18,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Laser operation, complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.18,0:12:34.38,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The bore path has been secured.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.38,0:12:36.38,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The Type D equipment is\Nfunctioning normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.88,0:12:38.89,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Unit 02 is in position to dispatch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.39,0:12:40.66,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.66,0:12:42.49,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Asuka, are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:44.06,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Anytime you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.06,0:12:45.56,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.84,0:12:56.37,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It looks hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.67,0:13:01.85,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Unit 02 is entering the lava.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.38,0:13:03.95,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Look at this, Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.78,0:13:07.26,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Giant Stroke Entry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.59,0:13:15.47,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Current depth: 170.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.47,0:13:16.69,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Speed of descent: 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:18.16,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,No problems detected.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.16,0:13:19.87,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Visibility is zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.87,0:13:21.46,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I can’t see a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.46,0:13:23.41,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Switching to CT monitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.17,0:13:28.51,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Even with this, the range of clarity is\Nno more than 120.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.01,0:13:33.75,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Depth is 400...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.11,0:13:35.81,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,450...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.81,0:13:37.18,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,500...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.18,0:13:38.91,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,550...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.91,0:13:40.11,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,600...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.11,0:13:41.29,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,650...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.56,0:13:48.72,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,900...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:50.56,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,950...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.56,0:13:51.73,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,1000...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.73,0:13:53.03,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,1020...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.03,0:13:54.84,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,We’re over the maximum safety depth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.90,0:13:57.46,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Depth is 1300.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.46,0:13:59.27,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Unit 02 has reached estimated\Ntarget level.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:00.20,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Asuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.20,0:14:01.20,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Can you see anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.67,0:14:04.01,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,No reactions detected.  It’s not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:06.51,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The lava circulation is faster\Nthan we thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.51,0:14:09.38,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The target’s velocity doesn’t\Nmatch our predictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.38,0:14:10.98,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hurry up and recalculate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.98,0:14:13.79,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Continue the operation.\NMaintain descent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:21.52,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Depth is 1350.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.52,0:14:23.02,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,1400...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.79,0:14:26.29,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,A crack has occurred on the\Nsecond coolant pipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.29,0:14:28.63,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Depth is 1480.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.63,0:14:30.77,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,We have exceeded the maximum\Nallowed depth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.77,0:14:33.50,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It hasn’t made contact with\Nthe target, yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.50,0:14:34.74,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.74,0:14:35.77,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,How’s it going, Asuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:39.37,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m okay.  I just want to finish this and\Ntake a shower, as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.37,0:14:42.31,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,There’s a nice hot spring near here.\NWe’ll hit it once this is finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.31,0:14:43.76,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Just hang in there a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.25,0:14:49.35,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Maximum allowed depth plus 120.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.75,0:14:54.22,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Eva Unit 02 has lost its\Nprogressive knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.22,0:14:56.39,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Maximum allowed depth plus 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.39,0:14:58.73,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Captain Katsuragi, we’ve got to stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.73,0:15:01.23,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten that there’s a\Nhuman being in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.23,0:15:03.90,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I am in charge of this operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.90,0:15:05.40,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Proceed, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.17,0:15:08.00,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Misato’s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.00,0:15:09.64,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m okay.  I can go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:17.41,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Depth 1780.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.41,0:15:19.39,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Unit 02 has reached the corrected\Ntarget depth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.12,0:15:24.62,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.59,0:15:29.62,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Target in sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.62,0:15:31.13,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Prepare to capture.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.26,0:15:35.53,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,All right, due to the motion of the\Nconvection current moving you\Nand the target...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:38.27,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...you’ll have just one chance\Nto make contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.27,0:15:40.40,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I know.  Just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.40,0:15:42.67,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,30 to contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:45.62,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Relative velocity 2.2.  On the axis.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.61,0:15:53.79,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The electromagnetic cage has been\Nspread.  No problems detected.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.28,0:15:55.82,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The target has been captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.59,0:15:59.09,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Nice, Asuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.59,0:16:03.22,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Operation completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.22,0:16:04.70,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m coming up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.26,0:16:11.63,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Asuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.63,0:16:15.30,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Who do you think you’re talking to?\NFear is often worse than danger itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.30,0:16:16.84,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It was an easy assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:21.35,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Boy, this isn’t a plug suit.\NIt’s a sauna suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.21,0:16:24.85,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I wanna take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:28.32,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The tension let loose all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.32,0:16:29.18,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.18,0:16:32.49,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You were scared about this operation\Ntoo, weren’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.49,0:16:36.42,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, yeah.  Because if it’d gone wrong,\Nit could’ve caused another disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.42,0:16:38.80,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Right, Second Impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.29,0:16:40.74,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Nobody would want to\Nrepeat that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.70,0:16:44.27,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What’s going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.67,0:16:51.31,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Oh, no!  It’s started to hatch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.31,0:16:52.81,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s much earlier than we predicted!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.31,0:16:54.04,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Status of the cage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.04,0:16:55.38,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,There’s no way it can withstand this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.85,0:17:01.26,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Abort the capture!  Jettison the cage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.49,0:17:05.75,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,We’re changing the operation!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:07.92,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Destroying the Angel is\Nnow top priority!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:11.03,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Unit 02, withdraw and\Nprepare for combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.03,0:17:12.53,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is what I’ve waited for!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.56,0:17:19.44,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Damn it!  I forgot I dropped the knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.40,0:17:21.90,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s right in front of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.57,0:17:24.07,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Releasing ballast!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.38,0:17:28.88,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.48,0:17:34.65,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is no good.  I’ve lost it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.65,0:17:37.59,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,In addition to that, I’ve got lousy\Nvisibility, I’m too hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.59,0:17:39.89,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...and this disgusting suit’s stuck to my\Nbody with sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.89,0:17:41.49,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This really sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:43.09,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.09,0:17:45.78,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,We’ll drop you Unit 01’s knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.78,0:17:46.69,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Catch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.69,0:17:48.20,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.93,0:17:49.80,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Oh, no!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.80,0:17:51.14,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Have you dropped it, Shinji?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:17:57.81,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Contact with knife, 40 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.81,0:17:59.54,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The Angel is approaching rapidly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.54,0:18:02.24,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,No!  Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.24,0:18:07.76,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hurry up!  Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.19,0:18:17.69,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What the hell?!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.26,0:18:24.37,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Unbelievable!  How can it open its\Nmouth in such an environment?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.37,0:18:26.04,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Its construction must be incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.27,0:18:32.51,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The left leg is damaged!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.51,0:18:34.01,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The heat shields!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.08,0:18:37.42,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Damn you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.52,0:18:44.80,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,If this thing can withstand such a\Nhigh-heat, high-pressure environment...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.80,0:18:47.19,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...then the progressive knife will\Nbe useless against it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.19,0:18:48.62,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Then what’s the solution?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.62,0:18:49.58,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I know!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.58,0:18:50.86,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Like the one earlier!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.86,0:18:53.53,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Eat this!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.50,0:18:57.57,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I understand!  Thermal expansion!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:19:01.10,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Transfer all coolant pressure to\Ncable three!!  Hurry!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.20,0:19:30.77,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’ve done it but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.43,0:19:34.57,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Is this the end?  Looks like that’s that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.08,0:19:47.58,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.22,0:19:53.56,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Idiot!  What a show off!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.59,0:20:02.50,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.50,0:20:05.23,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Are the NERV personnel here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.23,0:20:06.73,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.04,0:20:10.54,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I need your signature here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.77,0:20:14.11,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Thanks so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.11,0:20:15.52,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,From Mr. Kaji?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.01,0:20:17.51,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.38,0:20:23.42,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The bath’s over there, to the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.52,0:20:30.43,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This feels like heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:38.11,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade In & Out,{\fad(170,170)}I never thought a bath could\Nfeel this good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:41.14,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.14,0:20:42.70,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Y...yes, ma’am!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.70,0:20:44.81,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Would you throw me the\Nbody shampoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.81,0:20:47.08,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,We ran out of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.28,0:20:48.28,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.71,0:20:50.54,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Here it comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.54,0:20:52.05,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.32,0:20:55.45,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.45,0:20:58.09,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You idiot!  You dork, watch where\Nyou’re throwing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.09,0:20:59.69,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,S...sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.69,0:21:02.26,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,He hit me in my most essential part!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.26,0:21:03.76,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Let me take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.96,0:21:08.70,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Wow, your skin is so soft\Nand smooth, Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.66,0:21:11.80,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Don’t!  You’re tickling me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.80,0:21:13.30,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,How about right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:15.90,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Wow!  Don’t touch that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.90,0:21:17.94,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Come on, what gives?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.74,0:21:24.04,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade In,{\fad(170,0)}It expanded...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.04,0:21:25.63,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade Out,{\fad(0,170)}...how embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.09,0:21:38.59,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Oh, this?  I got this in\Nthe Second Impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.80,0:21:45.74,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You know all about my past, don’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.43,0:21:48.44,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, yeah.  It’s a part of my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.30,0:21:52.27,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s all ancient history now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.27,0:21:53.84,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,We should just forget.
