Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.21,0:23:07.95,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The Angels aren’t Commander Ikari’s\Nonly enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.52,0:23:13.99,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,When those who are displeased with\NNERV cut off Tokyo-3’s power supply...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.99,0:23:17.26,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...an Angel arrives at NERV\NHeadquarters to find it\Ncompletely locked up...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.26,0:23:19.13,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...with no modernized\Nfacilities operational.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.13,0:23:22.40,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Can three kids wandering through the\Nunderground labyrinth...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.40,0:23:24.93,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...make it to headquarters in time to\Nintercept the Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.93,0:23:28.04,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s the next episode,\N“In the Still Darkness.”
Dialogue: 5,0:23:28.04,0:23:30.78,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Video Text,You can expect more service\Nnext time too!
